The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business
 Saturday, April 24, 2004 				 Twins merger
Mumbai, April 23: Bharti Tele-Ventures, the holding company of all Sunil Mittal-promoted telecom ventures, today told stock exchanges it had decided to merge group firms Bharti Cellular and Bharti Infotel with itself. 																								The consolidation, on the companys agenda for some time, was approved at the board meeting that took stock of the companys numbers for the previous financial year.
